   <suppress>
      <notes><![CDATA[
      file name: installation-manager-api-1.2.1.Final.jar

      WildFly Installation Manager API is being incorrectly mapped to IBM Installation Manager and IBM Rational ClearCase.
      The POM contains developer metadata pointing to IBM (developer org), causing the scanner to incorrectly
      associate this with IBM products. This is WildFly's own installation manager API, not IBM's product.
      ]]></notes>
      <packageUrl regex="true">^pkg:maven/org\.wildfly\.installation\-manager/installation\-manager\-api@.*$</packageUrl>
      <cpe>cpe:/a:ibm:installation_manager</cpe>
      <cpe>cpe:/a:ibm:rational_clearcase</cpe>
   </suppress>
