    file name: grpc-api-1.70.0.jar

    False positive: This CVE affects gRPC-Go (Go language implementation), not grpc-api (Java implementation).
    WildFly uses the Java gRPC library which is a separate codebase from gRPC-Go.

    CVE-2026-33186 explicitly targets: cpe:2.3:a:grpc:grpc:*:*:*:*:*:go:*:*
    Our dependency is: pkg:maven/io.grpc/grpc-api (Java/Maven)

    https://github.com/grpc/grpc-go/security/advisories/GHSA-p77j-4mvh-x3m3
    ]]></notes>
    <packageUrl regex="true">^pkg:maven/io\.grpc/grpc-api@.*$</packageUrl>
    <cve>CVE-2026-33186</cve>
